<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r2l27">leute ſein ſulle / Laſſen wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> vviſʒen daʒ die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r2l28"><expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd Burgerin
                            <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jr hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r2l29">vnd kauffmanſchaft vor vns cʒu
