</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="64r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu der Newenstat an der Eysch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                            <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Kylian,
                                <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add>, und Gerhaus, die <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Haubnerin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        burgerin, wie daz man in etwievil hab und kauffmanschaft <add>in
                                    <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> stübich</add> bey ew bekümert und
                        auf <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hab und maine, daz die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> leute
                        sein sulle. Lassen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> wiszen, daz die
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und burgerin,
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir hab und kauffmanschaft vor uns czu
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz
                        die ir und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sey, also daz khein auszman
                                <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemein daran hab.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>rn</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und burgerin,
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir hab und kaufmanschaft on
                        hindernüsse <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> und ledig
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wölle, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
